</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Start Print job 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> During printing tape a piece of tape beside the media edge on the platen, as a reference, to see if the media is running straight through the printer. 
</p></li></ul><fig id="GUID-E789B918-968D-4FDF-9012-4A76C569B4F9" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-38E68F46-9E5D-41A1-9AF3-197E0F7DF20D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-38E68F46-9E5D-41A1-9AF3-197E0F7DF20D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-EC40CA6A-94BA-426F-AA19-34D6DAAFB113" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-906F39B9-6624-4901-B555-5BDCBAC3F9C9-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-906F39B9-6624-4901-B555-5BDCBAC3F9C9-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Function logging Ref B)</b>
